features: MATT JACKSON AEW ACTION FIGURE! The All Elite Wrestling Unrivaled Assortment features the highly detailed 6.5-inch pro-wrestling Matt Jackson action figure, making it an incredible addition to any collection!

PLAYABLE & DISPLAYABLE! Matt’s collectible figure is poseable with 25 points of articulation! You can pose the AEW wrestler in your favorite action shot, perfect for recreating your dream AEW roster match-up!
TRUE-TO-LIFE DETAILS! Matt Jackson’s likeness features character-authentic details, including body type and facial expression!
UNIQUE PRO-WRESTLING ACCESSORIES! It’s all in the details! The AEW collectible also includes a removable black and gold vest jacket accessory!
PERFECT GIFT FOR FANS! Jazwares’ AEW action figures make the perfect present for AEW fans everywhere!

COLLECT THEM ALL! The complete Series 3 action figure collection features Pac, Riho, Orange Cassidy, Darby Allin as well as the “Young Bucks” Matt Jackson and Nick Jackson, each with different accessories!
body.description: AEW Unrivaled Collection Series 3 ups the ante with the hottest lineup in pro wrestling with an all new Matt Jackson figure Recreate your favorite matchup with his 6.5-inch action figure As one-half of the tag team duo the ‘Young Bucks,’ Matt Jackson is also a co-holder of the AEW World Tag Team Championship. His brother, Nick Jackson, is also a part of this limited edition series Featuring a removable black and gold vest jacket accessory, the wrestler is ready to showcase his signature wrestling moves The complete AEW Unrivaled Series 3 includes Pac, Riho, Orange Cassidy, Darby Allin, and “Young Bucks” Matt Jackson and Nick Jackson. Also available are the highly collectible Riho Chase Variant and Darby Allin Rare Figure Each collectible boasts 25 points of articulation, authentically styled from the AEW Dynamite and PPV events Start your AEW collection today

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: ABOUT US Jazwares’ portfolio includes a variety of dynamic, wholly-owned and licensed brands like preschool powerhouses Blippi, Cabbage Patch Kids, CoComelon and Peppa Pig, unstoppable action and gaming brands like Fortnite, Halo, Micro Machines, Nerf, Pokémon and Roblox, leading lifestyle and entertainment brands like All Elite Wrestling (AEW), BLACKPINK, Blinger, UFC, musical property First Act, and beloved plush Hug-A-Pet and Squishmallows, just to name a few. With over 20 years of design, development and manufacturing expertise, Jazwares is an award-winning company with a progressive focus on identifying new trends and transforming them into high-quality products for consumers of all ages. Jazwares, which is headquartered in Sunrise, FL, has offices around the world and sells in over 100 countries. Since its inception in 1997, Jazwares continues to grow through the development of new products and the strategic acquisitions of companies like First Act, Russ Berrie, Zag Toys, Wicked Cool Toys and Kellytoy.
